The perfect gift.
一份很棒的礼物

2
00:00:03,494 --> 00:00:05,876
A girl trapped in a box.
一个困在盒子里的姑娘

3
00:00:06,890 --> 00:00:10,687
She only dances when someone else opens the lid,
当有人打开盖子

4
00:00:11,192 --> 00:00:14,443
when someone else winds her up.
上足发条 她才能跳舞

5
00:00:31,421 --> 00:00:33,840
If this is a story I'm telling,
如果这是我要讲的故事

6
00:00:34,472 --> 00:00:36,610
I must be telling it to someone.
我一定要说给某个人听

7
00:00:37,490 --> 00:00:39,389
